WEBVTT

00:01.040 --> 00:02.836
<i>Previously on</i> One Tree Hill.

00:02.920 --> 00:04.592
Somebody has a gun inside
and they're shooting.

00:04.680 --> 00:05.635
We're getting out of here, okay?

00:05.720 --> 00:06.755
Get away from the door.

00:06.840 --> 00:08.478
We gotta get you somewhere safe.
Come on.

00:08.560 --> 00:10.198
No, don't leave me, please.

00:10.280 --> 00:11.793
You're gonna tape a line
down the center of the room.

00:11.880 --> 00:12.915
Go on!

00:13.000 --> 00:14.319
If I say,

00:15.000 --> 00:16.877
"I love you" right now,

00:16.960 --> 00:18.712
will you hold it against me?

00:19.840 --> 00:20.909
Don't push me.

00:21.000 --> 00:22.035
He's not gonna do it!

00:22.120 --> 00:23.838
- Back him up!
- Listen to him.

00:24.000 --> 00:25.115
I promise you.

00:25.200 --> 00:27.589
Whoever steps into that hallway
is gonna die.

00:27.680 --> 00:29.352
It's never gonna be the same.

00:29.440 --> 00:31.192
This is wrong, man. All of this.

00:31.280 --> 00:32.314
This is your fault.

00:32.400 --> 00:33.628
I just wanted it to stop.

00:33.720 --> 00:34.914
Just take it all back.

00:35.000 --> 00:36.353
You got to let me try to talk to him.

00:36.440 --> 00:37.953
Jimmy, please.

00:38.160 --> 00:39.593
I'm sorry.

00:39.680 --> 00:40.715
No!

00:41.280 --> 00:42.269
<i>He's gone, Danny.</i>

00:42.360 --> 00:43.349
<i>He's gone.</i>

